data.description: Welcome to this charming single-family home situated in the quiet and desirable neighborhood of River Bluff. Features include 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and 1 half bath, generous size upstairs master suite, formal dining room, family room with wood burning fireplace, main level laundry, private back yard with storage building with electricity.  The property is minutes from historic downtown Monroe and with great schools this is an excellent choice for many families.  The current FHA loan is assumable for owner occupants who must qualify with M&T Mortgage.  You may of course secure new financing with the lender of your choice.  The property does need cosmetic updates like paint and flooring to make this a perfect home.  The listed price reflects the updates needed and is sold as-is.  The owner does have a dog in the property so showing appointments must be made with showingtime.
